TermDesc:
Resonance Rate is capped at 4 points.
- Casting Resonance Skill Duet of Seraphic Plumes recovers 1 points of Resonance Rate.
- Casting Resonance Liberation Heavenfall Edict - Overdrive recovers 1 points of Resonance Rate.
- When in Starlume Acceleration, casting Resonance Liberation Heavenfall Edict - Overdrive additionally recovers 1 points of Resonance Rate.
